<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
<meta charset="UTF-8">
<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
<link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Bebas+Neue&family=Barlow:wght@300;400;500;600&family=Cormorant+Garamond:ital,wght@0,400&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
<style>
*, *::before, *::after { margin: 0; padding: 0; box-sizing: border-box; }
:root {
  --charcoal: #111114; --red: #c1272d; --red-bright: #e63946;
  --cream: #f0ece4; --warm-white: #faf8f4; --slate: #6b6b78; --light-slate: #9a9aaa;
  --font-display: 'Bebas Neue', sans-serif;
  --font-body: 'Barlow', sans-serif;
  --font-accent: 'Cormorant Garamond', serif;
  --section-pad: clamp(80px, 10vw, 140px);
}
body { font-family: var(--font-body); background: var(--charcoal); color: var(--cream); -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; }
a { color: inherit; text-decoration: none; }
.container { max-width: 1320px; margin: 0 auto; padding: 0 clamp(20px, 4vw, 60px); }

.seasonal-cta { padding: var(--section-pad) 0; background: var(--charcoal); position: relative; overflow: hidden; }
.seasonal-cta__inner { position: relative; text-align: center; z-index: 2; }
.seasonal-cta__bg-text {
  position: absolute; top: 50%; left: 50%; transform: translate(-50%, -50%);
  font-family: var(--font-display); font-size: clamp(100px, 18vw, 280px);
  text-transform: uppercase; color: rgba(240,236,228,0.02);
  white-space: nowrap; pointer-events: none; z-index: 0; letter-spacing: 10px;
}

.section-tag { font-family: var(--font-body); font-weight: 500; font-size: 11px; letter-spacing: 4px; text-transform: uppercase; color: var(--red-bright); margin-bottom: 20px; display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 12px; }
.section-tag::before { content: ''; width: 24px; height: 1px; background: var(--red); }
.section-title { font-family: var(--font-display); font-size: clamp(40px, 6vw, 72px); line-height: 1; letter-spacing: 1px; text-transform: uppercase; color: var(--warm-white); margin-bottom: 20px; }
.section-title span { color: var(--red-bright); }

.seasonal-cta__sub { font-family: var(--font-accent); font-size: clamp(18px, 2vw, 22px); font-style: italic; color: var(--light-slate); max-width: 560px; margin: 0 auto 40px; line-height: 1.6; }
.seasonal-cta__actions { display: flex; gap: 16px; justify-content: center; flex-wrap: wrap; }
.seasonal-cta__note { margin-top: 24px; font-size: 13px; color: var(--slate); display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center; gap: 8px; }

.btn-primary {
  display: inline-flex; align-items: center; gap: 10px;
  padding: 16px 36px; background: var(--red); color: white;
  font-family: var(--font-body); font-weight: 600; font-size: 14px;
  letter-spacing: 1.5px; text-transform: uppercase;
  border: none; cursor: pointer; transition: all 0.3s ease;
  position: relative; overflow: hidden;
}
.btn-primary:hover { background: var(--red-bright); transform: translateY(-2px); box-shadow: 0 8px 30px rgba(193,39,45,0.4); }

.btn-ghost {
  display: inline-flex; align-items: center; gap: 10px;
  padding: 16px 32px; background: transparent; color: var(--cream);
  font-family: var(--font-body); font-weight: 500; font-size: 14px;
  letter-spacing: 1.5px; text-transform: uppercase;
  border: 1px solid rgba(240,236,228,0.2); cursor: pointer; transition: all 0.3s ease;
}
.btn-ghost:hover { border-color: var(--cream); background: rgba(240,236,228,0.06); }
</style>
</head>
<body>
<section class="seasonal-cta">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="seasonal-cta__inner">
      <div class="seasonal-cta__bg-text">BOOK NOW</div>
      <div class="section-tag" style="justify-content:center;">Summer 2026</div>
      <h2 class="section-title">KNOW WHEN TO <span>BOOK.</span></h2>
      <p class="seasonal-cta__sub">Around half of trips are booked within 10 days—but prime times don’t last that long. Check availability now and plan accordingly.</p>
      <div class="seasonal-cta__actions">
        <a href="https://fareharbor.com/embeds/book/baxstarfishing/items/309836/calendar/2026/04/?full-items=yes&back=https://www.baxstarfishing.com/" target="_top" class="btn-primary">
          Check Availability
          <svg width="16" height="16" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path d="M5 12h14M12 5l7 7-7 7"/></svg>
        </a>
        <a href="tel:+12185551234" class="btn-ghost">Call to Book</a>
      </div>
      <div class="seasonal-cta__note">
        <svg width="10" height="10" fill="#22c55e" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><circle cx="12" cy="12" r="10"/></svg>
        Cancel up to 24 hours before the trip when you add Trip Protection at checkout.
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
</body>
</html>
